dct_title_s: Salem River and Proposed Municipal Wharf
dct_description_sm: This map has insets showing the general plan for the city, another showing a cross section of the freight house, a cross section of the existing warehouse and a location map for the area. The map has rail lines for the West Jersey and Seashore Rail Road, Salem Branch Rail Road, and the Central Rail Road of New Jersey.
